}
for(t in 3:follow_up){

10 ICER

ICER <- matrix(rep(NA, PSA_samples), nrow=PSA_samples)
for(i in 1:PSA_samples){
ICER[i]  <- (Expected_total_cost_combi[i] - Expected_total_cost_mono[i]) / (Expected_LY_combi[i] - Expected_LY_mono[i])
}
